				"description": {
					"value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You have a hand free and are within melee reach of an opponent.</p><hr><p>You hook a foe's bootlaces together, pull their hat over their eyes, loosen their belt, or otherwise confound their mobility through an underhanded tactic. Attempt a @Check[thievery|defense:reflex] check against the target's Reflex DC.</p><hr><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 1} until they use an Interact action to end the impediment</p><p><strong>Success</strong> As critical success, but the condition ends automatically after 1 round.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> You fall @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone} as your attempt backfires.</p>",
